    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h2 id="获取window-terminal图标"><a href="#获取window-terminal图标" class="headerlink" title="获取window terminal图标"></a>获取window terminal图标</h2><p>鼠标右键图片另存为，保存到一个存放该图标的文件夹中<br><a href="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/terminal.ico" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="图标" class="fancybox"><img alt="图标" data-src="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/terminal.ico" class="lazyload" title="图标"></a></p><h2 id="添加注册表文件"><a href="#添加注册表文件" class="headerlink" title="添加注册表文件"></a>添加注册表文件</h2><p>新建一个.reg文件，文件名随意，里面添加下面的内容，之后再执行</p><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Directory\Background\shell\wt]</span><br><span class="line">@="Windows Terminal here"</span><br><span class="line">"Icon"="你的图标位置"</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\Directory\Background\shell\wt\command]</span><br><span class="line">@="C:\\Users\\[用户名]\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\WindowsApps\\wt.exe"</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><p>执行完之后,鼠标右键就有了window terminal<br><a href="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/Snipaste_2020-01-02_22-46-59.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/Snipaste_2020-01-02_22-46-59.png" class="lazyload" title></a></p><h2 id="修改配置"><a href="#修改配置" class="headerlink" title="修改配置"></a>修改配置</h2><p>打开window terminal ，点击settings<br><a href="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/setting.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/setting.png" class="lazyload" title></a><br>将”profiles”内所有startingDirectory改为null,没有的话自己创建一个，保存之后就大功告成了<br><a href="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/startingDirectory.png" data-fancybox="group" data-caption class="fancybox"><img alt data-src="http://q2t9w4d73.bkt.clouddn.com/terminal/startingDirectory.png" class="lazyload" title></a></p></body></html>]]></content>
    
